#summary Examples of Sets in Collections Ontology

=== Example Set.1: "Contributors of CO" ===

{{{
<http://purl.org/co/example/1/set/1>
 	a co:Set;
 	rdf:label "Collections Ontology Contributors" ;
 	co:element <http://www.hcklab.org/foaf.rdf#me> ;
 	co:element :a1 ;
 	co:element :a2 .
 		
<http://www.hcklab.org/foaf.rdf#me> 
    a foaf:Person .
    
:a1
    a foaf:Person ;
    foaf:firstName "Marco" ;
    foaf:lastName "Ocana" .
    
:a2
    a foaf:Person ;
    foaf:firstName "Silvio" ;
    foaf:lastName "Peroni" .
}}}
